| Component | Location | Pattern | Notes |
|-----------|----------|---------|-------|
| **Token type** | src/tok.h:35-48 | `#define RES_ROLL N` | Add after RES_PICK=12 |
| **Tokenizer** | src/tok.h:94-137 | Add to `lookup_reserved()` | Match "roll" keyword |
| **AST Node** | src/parse.h:16 | NODE_MONAD (reuse) | Already supports monadic ops |
| **Parser** | src/parse.h:306-312 | Already handles monadic | No changes needed |
| **Evaluator** | src/eval.h:565-632 | Add RES_ROLL case | Generates random 0..N-1 |
| **PRNG state** | src/eval.h:14-16 | Add `int lcg_seed;` | Global LCG seed |
| **Quad variable** | src/eval.h:376-401 | Create qRL_shadow | For `[]RL <- N` |
| **Hardware timing** | src/io.h:14-44 | Modify `io_getline()` | Could capture UART timing |
| **Docs** | docs/ | Create randomness.md | Explain LCG + qRL |

